OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1773223748
OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,FCaledonian Road in Islington is hoped
OL,8,Fto reopen today after it was flooded,
OL,9,Fbut local businesses fear they will
OL,10,Fhave to wait much longer before they
OL,11,Fcan run as usual.
OL,13,FMore than 40 businesses are either
OL,14,Fstill closed - or not yet back to
OL,15,Fnormal.
OL,17,FThousands of people were affected by
OL,18,Fthe flooding almost two weeks ago,
OL,19,Fleaving many with uninhabitable homes
OL,20,Fand businesses in ruin.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
