OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,FWatch the initial impact of the flood
OL,8,Fon Tuesday 24th February:
OL,10,FRepairs to the water mains were
OL,11,Fcompleted over the weekend.
OL,13,FWondwosen Zeleke owns a local
OL,14,FEthiopian shop, which he has been told
OL,15,Fis one of the worst affected on the
OL,16,Fstreet.
OL,18,FHe said: "The shop is totally damaged
OL,19,Fwith the flooding.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
