OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,F"Still now we don't have electricity,
OL,8,Fyou can't work here. The shop is still
OL,9,Fshut because can't work in these
OL,10,Fconditions. "
OL,12,FWondwosen is now trying to set up an
OL,13,Fonline business for Heraan Ltd to keep
OL,14,Fconnected with his customers.
OL,16,FHe says that the shop has lost between
OL,17,F#40,000 and #50,000.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
