OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,FHe continued: "Honestly last time we
OL,8,Fhad a meeting about it, they were
OL,9,Fsaying it might take almost six weeks
OL,10,Fto clear the basement.
OL,12,F"For sure it will take two months, two
OL,13,Fmonths at least."
OL,15,FShop owner Babu Rajah is facing
OL,16,Fsimilar challenges. His fast food
OL,17,Fbusiness, Ten Ten Chicken, has been
OL,18,Fopen for less than a year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
