OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,FHe said, "It's going to close, they
OL,8,Fsay, for four weeks, it's affected our
OL,9,Fbusiness, it's already been two weeks
OL,10,Fnow."
OL,12,FHe told ITV News London that the
OL,13,Fdamage will cost him over #50,000.
OL,15,FThames Water said that work to fully
OL,16,Freinstate the area is continuing and
OL,17,Fthey hope to complete this by the end
OL,18,Fof the day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
