OL,3,CMore than 40 businesses closed or
OL,4,Cstruggling after flood on Caledonian
OL,5,CRoad
OL,7,FIn an update posted today, they also
OL,8,Fsaid "Our customer and community teams
OL,9,Fare continuing to provide support
OL,10,Flocally.
OL,12,F"Our Customer Support Hub at All
OL,13,FSaints Church, Caledonian Road, N1 9QW
OL,14,Fwill open today at 10:00 and will
OL,15,Fclose at 16:00.
OL,17,F"We'd like to sincerely thank everyone
OL,18,Ffor their patience and continued
OL,19,Fsupport while we carried out these
OL,20,Fessential repairs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
